{"tid":2101112,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"莎莎收銀員確診 油塘分店將停業14日消毒","createTime":"2020-07-09T14:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T14:48:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a404017374caa4994bc6cd2afe99b4ca698e89bc","tid":2101112,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:14:30.000Z","msg":"莎莎位於油塘大本型1樓的分店，有1名收銀員確診新冠肺炎，由即日起暫停營業14天，進行徹底清潔及消毒。<br />\n<br />\n莎莎表示，該名員工自上周日（5日）起，因病請假一直沒有上班，而店內所有員工及與該名員工有接觸的其他相關職員，將在家隔離14天。同時呼籲近日曾經光顧及到訪該分店的人士及顧客，留意個人健康狀況，如有需要請致電衞生防護中心熱線。"},{"pid":"201bec7a6fb492fc20f62ebb4a5518d03f8499de","tid":2101112,"uid":136797,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TTQ1ueY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTTQ1ueY.gif&h=c93fcc94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e1e384ab58e75022fc92628688f4fdad8c6e2f0","tid":2101112,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"藍店回力鏢"},{"pid":"360ec5eb874cb09cfa9e6e89bf5c2c7761756b7e","tid":2101112,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:16:31.000Z","msg":"油糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60f949e07d57527b21a8b408c3426cb4cbc9e91","tid":2101112,"uid":65074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:17:17.000Z","msg":"藍屍感染圈"},{"pid":"75f96a0d33a09331e6567b1703f12fa5ca036732","tid":2101112,"uid":68080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:18:37.000Z","msg":"油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n莎莎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714bb353ca6dd3583ce449f510034e6a3e92832b","tid":2101112,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75f96a0d33a09331e6567b1703f12fa5ca036732","tid":210